claim.claim-text:
1. A sport fishing system comprising:
(a) a rod and reel, including fishing line;
(b) at least one fishing lure or natural bait;
(c) a controlled released fish attractant configured to be subsequently applied to coat the at least one lure or bait while fishing, wherein said controlled release fish attractant includes: (i) an attractant and (ii) a substantially hydrophobic, film forming release agent which is a silicone-based polymer having about 6% by weight silicone polymer; and
(d) an applicator for applying said controlled released fish attractant to said fishing lure or natural bait while fishing.
